<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent65969c749a77497da74ea3797b6b3cd0">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="The Churchill Hospital, outside the main entrance" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=475"/>
</div>
</div>
<p>The <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/hospitals/churchill/default.aspx">Churchill Hospital</a> in Headington, Oxford, is the site of the <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/cancer/">Oxford Cancer Centre</a> and a centre for <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/services/departments/renal/oxford-kidney-unit/default.aspx">renal</a> and <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/services/departments/renal/transplant/default.aspx">transplant</a> services, medical and surgical services, <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/cancer/services/oncology.aspx">oncology</a>, <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/services/departments/specialist-medicine/dermatology/default.aspx">dermatology</a>, <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/services/departments/specialist-medicine/haemophilia/default.aspx">haemophilia</a>, <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/services/departments/specialist-medicine/infectious-diseases/default.aspx">infectious diseases</a>, <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/services/departments/specialist-medicine/respiratory-medicine/default.aspx">respiratory medicine</a>, medical genetics, <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/cancer/palliative-care.aspx">palliative care</a> and <a href="http://www.ouh.nhs.uk/services/departments/sexual-health/default.aspx">sexual health</a>.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
